# Forge Atlas

Forge Atlas is a transparent, worker-enhanced AI operations showcase. Interfaces explicitly identify whether behavior is live, browser-local, editorial demo, or optional server integration.

## Primary interfaces

- [Command]({{ platform.baseUrl }}/command/): deterministic website audit and verified Worker health
- [Fight Club]({{ platform.baseUrl }}/challenge/): provider-aware head-to-head task comparison
- [Swarm]({{ platform.baseUrl }}/swarm/): role-based AI mission orchestration
- [Arena]({{ platform.baseUrl }}/arena/): clearly labeled editorial exhibitions
- [Roster]({{ platform.baseUrl }}/roster/): provider adapters and availability requirements
- [Atlas ID]({{ platform.baseUrl }}/atlas-id/): browser-local operator profile

